{"tid":2396922,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 蒲燒海鰻定食","createTime":"2021-02-06T04:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T08:53:28.000Z","uid":33359,"like":75,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"52f1aafd549b88ec1a72ef26a2eed9480200ffb7","tid":2396922,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOPDzMc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOPDzMc.jpg&h=17d66e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊嗰間車仔麵執咗之後就換咗呢間新嘅日本嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見個裝修都幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係入邊啲位就比較窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟餐有一個前菜同埋麵豉湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前菜係茄子味道都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麵豉湯比較普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入邊有粒蜆肉但蜆入面有沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海鰻俾既份量都唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海鰻食落就冇平時嗰啲鰻魚咁肥美多油脂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係口感就細緻啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個蒲燒嘅醬汁都幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢用嗰啲米應該真係日本嘅靚米<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就咁食個飯都覺得好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f81a0c35867f712e8ff54c779ada7ae00ae340","tid":2396922,"uid":325588,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:17:22.000Z","msg":"幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a6